@Davidnet , ssd_mobilenet_v1 and ssd_mobilenet_v2 models are running on android mobile devices, not on desktop GPU.
I found the reason why kernel size of box_predictor is 1 in the ssd_mobilenet_v1. but kernel size of box_predictor is 3 in the ssd_mobilenet_v2.

body:
@Davidnet , ssd_mobilenet_v1 and ssd_mobilenet_v2 models are running on android mobile devices, not on desktop GPU.
I found the reason why kernel size of box_predictor is 1 in the ssd_mobilenet_v1. but kernel size of box_predictor is 3 in the ssd_mobilenet_v2.
